description: The Math History Trivia skill is the most fun you'll ever have with math! This skill will ask you questions that challenge you to think about math in an all new light that you never had! Questions include where does algebra originate, who founded calculus, and more! You will get to enjoy challenging yourself with your own knowledge of mathematical vocabulary and historic knowledge.
name: Math Trivia
shortDescription: The Math History Trivia skill will ask you questions about math that require NO math skills!
